message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which has been meticulously designed to meet your needs and exceed your expectations. This exceptional item is valued at $12000 to us, reflecting its high quality, unique features, and the expertise that went into its creation. Considering its unparalleled benefits, I would like to extend an exclusive offer to you for $10000. This is an opportunity to acquire a top-tier product at a competitive price, tailored specifically for individuals who appreciate excellence. Please let me know if you're interested in discussing this further.
